## Using compiler-$(environment) for app-foo/bar
# app-foo/bar compiler-clang

## Clang: Basic Setup (https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Clang#Basic_setup)
# compiler-clang: build with a general Clang environment
net-libs/libtorrent-rasterbar compiler-clang #qbittorrent wont build with clang-lto enabled here
sys-libs/compiler-rt compiler-clang #doesnt use lto
sys-libs/llvm-libunwind compiler-clang #doesnt use lto
